description: My Biggest Fan allows you to ask for compliments. You'll definitely feel better about yourself after hearing some of the great things your biggest fan has to say about you. To get started, you can say "Alexa, ask my biggest fan for a compliment."
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask My Biggest Fan for a compliment
Alexa, tell My Biggest Fan to give me a compliment
Alexa, talk to My Biggest Fan
name: My Biggest Fan
shortDescription: I'm your biggest fan. Ask me for a compliment and you'll come to realize how amazing you truly are.
